author: Rowan
text:
What a season its been from being -21 points to still staying up until the 43rd game.

So proud of this club. The togetherness of the fans the players the staff and everything.

Now time to rebuild and come back stronger.

Up The Rams @dcfcofficial #dcfc

text: having seen what’s happened so far and actually realising we might not be a club next month is actually heart aching i can’t actually imagine what i’d do without derby, the amount of memories i’ve had supporting this club and for it to be taken away like that it would be horrible
